reviews.review_description:
Bewilderness is a beautiful showcase for how mixed reality / augmented reality can provide enjoyment and memorable experiences right now with current tech on the Quest Platform! It has gorgeous visuals and a soothing audio score that really sets the mood. The Eagle is beautifully rendered and almost intimidating! The new update even includes bees (that you can control). This is a must own. I have uploaded a mixed reality video of this experience on youtube to give you all a better idea of truly how magnificent it is. Look it up on youtube! 

https://youtu.be/I2m-hFI1nKI

